1
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:27,980
How long do you plan to stay this time, Mr. An?

2
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,480
I haven't decided yet this time.

3
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,479
I'll go back when the group needs me.

4
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:35,170
You still can't forget your sweetheart, huh?

5
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:37,160
No.

6
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:38,840
It's been so long.

7
00:00:39,480 --> 00:00:40,610
It's time to forget.

8
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:42,120
Then you come back every year

9
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,440
just to see me?

10
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:45,080
That scares me a little.

11
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,440
Uncle He.

12
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:48,080
Stop teasing me.

13
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,840
The group has business here.

14
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,440
Can't I come back for a visit?

15
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:52,280
Sure.

16
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,690
Then I'll show you my old business.

17
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:14,960
Boss.

18
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:15,820
The usual spot.

19
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,720
Okay, boss.

20
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,480
Uncle He.

21
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,160
Are you completely hands-off now?

22
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,840
I never really managed anything.

23
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,840
Opening a coffee shop

24
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,100
is just a hobby of mine.

25
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,480
This hobby saved me back then.

26
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,400
Thank you.

27
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,640
Don't mention it.

28
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,840
Speaking of back then,

29
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,600
I have something to show you.

30
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,080
Come.

31
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:38,520
Hello, fans.

32
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,880
It's fate.

33
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:41,120
Later,

34
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,440
I ran into Yin Zixi again.

35
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,640
She was transitioning into an information anchor,

36
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,440
and I happened to be able to help.

37
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,120
For the sake of my nephew's happiness,

38
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,720
I still had to step in.

39
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:53,370
Isn't the one who leaked this our subsidiary?

40
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:56,479
Regarding the incident at the Cloud Data Integration Center,

41
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,759
I have some internal leaks, especially about the scene.

42
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,759
This isn't the clue I provided.

43
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,320
There's a problem with this report.

44
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:03,050
I need to review the situation.

45
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:12,300
Help me find out who is in charge of the Yunshu Integration Center.

46
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,760
Okay, quiet down first.

47
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,360
Does everyone think it's a bit strange?

48
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,240
Actually,

49
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,600
it's not strange at all.

50
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,720
Because I provided this news report.

51
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,970
What's wrong, Uncle He?

52
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,040
Zixi,

53
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:40,420
the report that got you trending is fake.

54
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,560
Fake?

55
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,880
This is a frame-up.

56
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,880
The report differs from the actual situation.

57
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,720
They only gave the news to your company.

58
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,600
I suspect someone is targeting you.

59
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,920
Get your person in charge out here.

60
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,200
You made us trend on social media.

61
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,480
I need an explanation for this today.

62
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:56,720
What's that sound? Hello?

63
00:02:57,880 --> 00:03:00,920
Yin Zixi, long time no see.

64
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,360
Where is she now?

65
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,260
I'll send you the address now.

66
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:07,880
Hello?

67
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,560
Arrange a car for me.

68
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:11,320
I'll send the address later.

69
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,090
How about driving this one?

70
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,200
Are your driving skills still okay?

71
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,360
Yin Zixi. Yin Zixi.

72
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,960
What are you waiting for?

73
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,720
I will handle the matter myself.

74
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:46,240
And I will get my account back.

75
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:55,520
Xihai University News.

76
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,240
Look.

77
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,410
It's you, right?

78
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,920
This is me.

79
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,420
Why don't I remember it at all?

80
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,800
Zixi.

81
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,120
The test results show nothing serious.

82
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,320
The patient just needs more rest.

83
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,560
Maybe she's under too much work pressure.

84
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,890
Let her have a good rest.

85
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,540
Thank you, Doctor.

86
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,530
You're welcome.

87
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,360
Here.

88
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,520
Who is that?

89
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,560
Why did he greet you?

90
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,820
He probably mistook me for someone else.

91
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,640
All right.

92
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,640
See how it turned out.

93
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,210
Congratulations on your graduation.

94
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,040
Thank you.

95
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,280
Zixi, who is this guy?

96
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,520
He is so handsome.

97
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,640
I don't know him.

98
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,810
He seems to know you.

99
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,960
Hello?

100
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,400
Okay, got it.

101
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,800
Zixi.

102
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,320
Long time no see.

103
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,290
Long time no see.

104
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,600
Casting Director Xi Chongjing

105
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,520
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

106
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,480
Production Vehicle Yi Mingle

107
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,440
Yitong
